  "replication_notes": "To replicate this aesthetic, start with a black or dark gray background. Choose a clean sans-serif typeface for body text and headings. Use ample whitespace to separate content blocks. Implement a minimal navigation with a hamburger menu for smaller screens. Keep the color palette limited to black, white, and potentially a single accent color. Consider adding subtle animations to enhance user engagement.",
